{
  "name": "FTC-WF-009_onboarding-miembro",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## FTC-WF-009 | Onboarding de Nuevo Miembro\n\n**Descripcion:** Automatiza el proceso de onboarding cuando una empresa cambia su estado a \"Activo\" en la base de datos de Empresas. Envia email de bienvenida, crea tareas de seguimiento y notifica al equipo via Slack.\n\n**Owner:** Operaciones\n**Folder:** /Operaciones\n**Criticidad:** Media\n**Fecha de creacion:** 2025-02-18\n**Version:** 1.0.0\n\n**Trigger:** Polling cada 5 minutos sobre Notion DB Empresas (Estado = Activo)\n\n**Dependencias:**\n- Notion: DB Empresas, DB Contactos, DB Tareas\n- Gmail: Cuenta corporativa FinteChile\n- Slack: Canal #ops-fintechile\n\n**Variables de entorno requeridas:**\n- NOTION_DB_EMPRESAS_ID\n- NOTION_DB_CONTACTOS_ID\n- NOTION_DB_TAREAS_ID\n- SLACK_CHANNEL_OPS\n- EMAIL_FROM",
        "height": 520,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "sticky-metadata",
      "name": "Workflow Metadata",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -200,
        -100
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "pollTimes": {
          "item": [
            {
              "mode": "everyX",
              "value": 5,
              "unit": "minutes"
            }
          ]
        },
        "event": "pagedUpdated",
        "simple": true,
        "databaseId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "={{ $env.NOTION_DB_EMPRESAS_ID }}",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "conditions": {
          "options": [
            {
              "key": "Estado",
              "type": "select",
              "condition": "equals",
              "returnType": "string",
              "value": "Activo"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "notion-trigger",
      "name": "Trigger: Empresa Activa",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.notionTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        340,
        260
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "notionApi": {
          "id": "notion-credentials",
          "name": "Notion account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "databasePage",
        "operation": "getAll",
        "databaseId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "={{ $env.NOTION_DB_CONTACTOS_ID }}",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "returnAll": false,
        "limit": 1,
        "filterType": "formula",
        "filters": {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "key": "Empresa",
              "type": "relation",
              "condition": "contains",
              "returnType": "string",
              "value": "={{ $json.id }}"
            },
            {
              "key": "Tipo",
              "type": "select",
              "condition": "equals",
              "returnType": "string",
              "value": "Principal"
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "AND"
        },
        "simple": true
      },
      "id": "get-contacto",
      "name": "Get Contacto Principal",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.notion",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
